### Test API Endpoints
### You can use this file with REST Client extension in VS Code, or copy these to Postman/Insomnia

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Signup
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "testpassword123"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "testpassword123"
}

### Get Profile (requires auth token from login response)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### List Missions (requires auth token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/missions
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Rewards (requires auth token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/rewards
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### Refresh Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "refreshToken": "YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
}

